DISCLAIMER — Third-party Service Terms of Use

This software includes a Chrome extension that reads purchase history from
Coupang (coupang.com) and Naver Pay (pay.naver.com) within the user's own
authenticated browser session. No credentials are stored or transmitted; data
is only posted to a local server running on the user's own machine.

Use of this tool is at the user's own discretion and risk. The author makes no
warranty that this usage complies with the current Terms of Service of Coupang,
Naver, or any other third-party platform. Users are solely responsible for
reviewing and complying with the applicable terms of those services.

This software does not transmit any personal or financial data to any external
server. All data remains on the user's local machine.
